"<https://certbot.eff.org/#ubuntuxenial-apache>`__."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-ssl-http2-apache2.rst:13
msgid ""
"If Let’s Encrypt is enabled, forward port 80 through a firewall, with "
"`Forward80To443 <https://docs.mattermost.com/administration/config-"
"settings.html#forward-port-80-to-443>`__ ``config.json`` setting set to "
"``true`` to complete the Let’s Encrypt certification."
