msgid ""
"Once installed, run ``$ certbot --apache`` and follow the guide. "
"Afterwards you should find a new configuration file in ``/etc/apache2"
"/sites-available`` which should follow the format ``mysubdomain.mydomain"
".com-le-ssl.conf``."
